divs: sighting detailsdownloading the photographs from my digital camera i noticed the strange object over the river. i didn't see it while taking the picture. location is near twickenham, west of london, direction north-east. the object on the left side over the trees is an airplane. heathrow lies some miles to the west, twenty minutes later i shot some photographs of landing airplanes, they were flying very low, direction east-west. the ufo reminds me of the one reported 10\09\07 on your website from montserrat in spain (with picture dfsc5825.jpg)
